            android:layout_marginStart="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="16dp"
            android:layout_marginEnd="16dp"
            android:layout_marginRight="16dp"
            android:text="       Voting is maybe the most important because it allows for real policy changes. Vote in your primaries to make sure you elect officials who are in support of bills and laws that support groups that need the protection of the law. Vote in the presidential election for a candidate that treats all human beings as equal and is not in an active effort to take certain groups of people’s rights away. Remember that YOU have a voice, so speak up and vote."
